{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"daaebb875c","title":"给李达的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"35b55aa7c6","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":27,"articleId":"daaebb875c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"6e101bce3e","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"daaebb875c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李达撰写的《<实践论>解说》一书，得到毛泽东本人的关心和赞赏。1952年3月，李达将第二部分打印稿寄呈毛泽东审正。这是毛泽东给他的回信。"}],"contents":[{"id":"880bfc9888","type":"title","text":"给李达的信！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"daaebb875c"},{"id":"6e101bce3e","type":"paragraph","text":"鹤鸣兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"daaebb875c"},{"id":"9bc5f2b363","type":"paragraph","text":"两次来信及附来《（实践论》解说》第二部分，均收到了。谢谢你！解说的第一部分也在刊物上看到了。这个解说极好，对于用通俗的言语宣传唯物论有很大的作用。待你的第三部分写完并发表之后，应当出一单行本，以广流传。第二部分中论帝国主义和教条主义、经验主义的那两页上有一点小的修改，请加的。如已发表，请在印单行本时修改好了","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"daaebb875c"},{"id":"33840510b2","type":"paragraph","text":"关于辩证唯物论的通俗宣传，过去做得太少，而不满足广大工人干部和青年学生的追切希望，希望你多多写些文章。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"daaebb875c"},{"id":"255d2f0556","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"daaebb875c"},{"id":"3abf26c29b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"daaebb875c"},{"id":"dcf3847181","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年三月二十七日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"daaebb875c"},{"id":"f399c8300c","type":"paragraph","text":"《实践论》中将太平天国放在排外主义一起说不妥，出选集时，拟加修改，此处暂仍回原。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanj